**Netflix**

Netflix, Inc. is an American [over-the-top media service](/Over-the-top_media_service) and [subscription video on demand](/Video_on_demand) ([SVOD](/SVOD)) service that distributes original and acquired films and television programs across a multitude of genres. Available in an astonishing 50 languages, it's a testament to the global reach of digital content, though one might wonder if the sheer volume dilutes the impact.

